    <section class="about">
      <h2>About / Author Statement</h2>
      <p>
        I am a science journalist and medical writer with a PhD in life sciences. My work focuses on the intersection of biomedical research, public health policy, and real‑world human consequences.
      </p>
      <p>
        Trained as a researcher and working as a long‑form nonfiction writer, I aim to translate complex scientific evidence into rigorous, accessible narratives without oversimplifying uncertainty.
      </p>
      <p>
        Juan Li 博士拥有发育生物学博士学位，曾在国际医学院和顶尖临床研究机构接受系统科研训练。她长期从事科学传播与医学写作，致力于将前沿科研成果转化为高质量公共知识。
      </p>
